### Test Category APIs

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1

### 1. Create Root Category - Electronics
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories/create-category
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "slug": "electronics",
  "description": "Electronic devices and accessories",
  "parentCategory": null,
  "order": 1
}

### 2. Create Root Category - Fashion
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories/create-category
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fashion",
  "slug": "fashion",
  "description": "Clothing and fashion accessories",
  "parentCategory": null,
  "order": 2
}

### 3. Create Subcategory - Men under Fashion
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories/create-category
