### 6. Get All Categories (Flat List)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### 7. Get Category Tree (Hierarchical)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/tree

### 8. Get Root Categories Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/root

### 9. Get Single Category with Subcategories - Men
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/men

### 10. Get Subcategories of Fashion
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/fashion/subcategories

### 11. Get Category Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/stats

### 12. Update Category
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/categories/men
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated men's fashion description",
  "order": 2
}

### 13. Get Products by Category - Men
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/men?page=1&limit=12

### 14. Get Products by Category with Subcategory Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/men?subCategory=shirt&page=1&limit=12

### 15. Get Products by Category with Price Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/electronics?minPrice=500&maxPrice=2000

### 16. Search within Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/category/men?searchTerm=casual

### 17. Get Best Seller Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/best-sellers?limit=10

### 18. Get Featured Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/featured?limit=10

### 19. Delete Category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/test-category
